"L_max=10000 across all k.  No discontinuity, no nonlinearity," . cr
"no critical exponent." . cr
cr
"Self-ref factor is a binary STEP (0 → scope·L_max), not a smooth" . cr
"phase transition — topological indicator, not critical phenomenon." . cr
cr
"HONEST NEGATIVE RESULT: the Φ_PA family as currently defined does" . cr
"NOT exhibit phase-transition behaviour.  Tononi-IIT-style Φ-" . cr
"criticality (Mediano 2019) is not replicated by phi-pa / phi-bidir" . cr
"/ phi-pa-witness; all three are degree-polynomial × self-loop-step." . cr
cr
